{"tid":1564933,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"在這個動盪時代，用電子遊戲回顧前瞻香港政治","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:10:42.000Z","uid":321748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"413a4143fb41d28d89c81a592a305a8612dabe51","tid":1564933,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hongkonginvideogames.blogspot.com/2019/09/politics.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkonginvideogames.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F09%2Fpolitics.html&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=4199d95e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hongkonginvideogames.blogspot.com/2019/09/politics.html</a><br />\n<br />\n即使題材敏感，香港政治仍可見於部分電玩香港世界中。令人驚訝的是，遊戲世界記下的，不僅現代香港歷史中的種種重要政治事件，還包括這些關鍵時刻的政治話題。 本文將探討這些政治事件和話題，以及它們對這城市的意義。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAqJDRc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAqJDRc.jpg&h=ee2680e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74a8a51dc66a2555ca9332d090df8792e23e61f6","tid":1564933,"uid":25185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"【 突發】和理塞 商場篇 終於出爐!922第一彈約定你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG :<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=1d3aada3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEgVehN8bY_NbBDM8g</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Whua26P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhua26P.jpg&h=0a307b31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0SzLka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0SzLka.jpg&h=aa4ea6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6d1717f880a3550d27a00062cb2c81990d05bce","tid":1564933,"uid":123991,"